# Task 14 – Dashboard & Reports Navigation

## Project

**Virtual Agent–Driven SLA Breach Awareness & Justification System**

---

## Objective

This task creates ServiceNow reports to analyze SLA breaches, acknowledgements, assignment groups, pending justifications, and SLA trends. These reports will later be added to the SLA Governance Dashboard.

---

## Navigation

**Platform Analytics Administration → Reports → Create New**

---

## Reports Created

| Report Name | Visualization |
|-------------|---------------|
| SLA Breaches by Reason | Pie |
| SLA Breaches by Assignment Group | Bar |
| Acknowledged vs Unacknowledged Breaches | Pie |
| Top Assignees with SLA Violations | Bar |
| Pending Justifications | List |
| SLA Performance Trend | Bar |

---

## Deliverables

- Six ServiceNow Reports
- Report Configurations
- Report Screenshots
- Dashboard Preparation

---

## Expected Outcome

The reports provide real-time insights into SLA governance and support dashboard creation for monitoring SLA performance and compliance.

---

## Status

**Completed**

